{"about_the_game":"<strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Take a Coffee Break While Death Awaits.</h2></strong><br>In Grim's Gambit, step into the shoes of Nox, who faces an unexpected twist of fate\u2014trading death for a life behind the counter of an enigmatic coffee shop within the eerie Stygian Keep. As Nox, you're sentenced to an otherworldly coffee shop in the desolate Stygian Keep instead of facing death. With amnesia clouding your past, you'll navigate a series of interactive puzzles and engage with unique characters to piece together your story. Experience a blend of dark mystery and quirky humor as you uncover secrets, confront existential themes, and redefine what it means to be alive in a world suspended between realms.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2748880/extras/skulliverchapter1.gif?t=1721868373\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Death Denied, Coffee Supplied: Your New Role in the Underworld!</h2><br>In Chapter 2 of Grim's Gambit, players continue Nox's thrilling journey through the Stygian Keep. Following the chaotic and darkly humorous events of the coffee shop, Nox faces new challenges and uncovers deeper mysteries. As he navigates through the Stygian Keep, he must manage the bustling demands of the coffee shop, meet intriguing new characters, and investigate the hidden secrets of this eerie realm.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2748880/extras/coffee.gif?t=1721868373\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2748880/extras/skulliver.gif?t=1721868373\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">chapter 1 &amp; 2 Available Now!</h2></h2></h2><u>For development and game updates, follow our official Instagram Page: @grimsgambit</u>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2748880/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1